## 🎯 Success Criteria

**A task is complete when:**
1. ✅ Design approved by user
2. ✅ Implementation matches design 95%+
3. ✅ All API endpoints working
4. ✅ Zero TypeScript errors
5. ✅ All states handled (loading, error, success, empty)
6. ✅ Mobile responsive
7. ✅ Tested with backend running
8. ✅ User can complete the full flow

